trans-unit.source: Represents the collection of selection choices in a <see cref="T:System.Windows.Forms.DataGridViewComboBoxCell" />.

You can retrieve <xref:System.Windows.Forms.DataGridViewComboBoxCell.ObjectCollection> objects from the <xref:System.Windows.Forms.DataGridViewComboBoxCell.Items%2A?displayProperty=nameWithType> property or the <xref:System.Windows.Forms.DataGridViewComboBoxColumn.Items%2A?displayProperty=nameWithType> property.
trans-unit.target: 검색할 수 있습니다 <xref:System.Windows.Forms.DataGridViewComboBoxCell.ObjectCollection> 에서 개체는 <xref:System.Windows.Forms.DataGridViewComboBoxCell.Items%2A?displayProperty=nameWithType> 속성 또는 <xref:System.Windows.Forms.DataGridViewComboBoxColumn.Items%2A?displayProperty=nameWithType> 속성입니다.

trans-unit.source: If <xref:System.Windows.Forms.DataGridViewComboBoxCell.Sorted%2A> is `false`, then the `index` value represents the position at which the `item` value is inserted.
trans-unit.target: 경우 <xref:System.Windows.Forms.DataGridViewComboBoxCell.Sorted%2A> 은 `false`, 하면 `index` 값 되는 위치를 나타냅니다.는 `item` 값이 삽입 됩니다.

trans-unit.source: If <xref:System.Windows.Forms.DataGridViewComboBoxCell.Sorted%2A> is `true`, then `index` is ignored and `item` is placed in the collection in a position determined by the sorting order.
trans-unit.target: 경우 <xref:System.Windows.Forms.DataGridViewComboBoxCell.Sorted%2A> 은 `true`, 다음 `index` 는 무시 됩니다 및 `item` 정렬 순서에 따라 결정 된 위치에 있는 컬렉션에 배치 됩니다.
